## VISUAL FOUNDATIONS

### Colors
- **Primary Blue (Sky):** `#20bcff` — brand signature. Nav background, buttons, links, logo.
- **Deep Blue:** `#0092d2` — hover states on CTAs, secondary blue accents.
- **Near-Black:** `#2a3135` — all body text, headings on white.
- **Orange:** `#f16322` — circular photo backgrounds (profile stories), accent highlights.
- **Yellow/Gold:** `#fbad18` — accent highlights, stat callouts.
- **Purple:** `#88206a` — occasional accent; secondary category use.
- **Dark Green:** `#005332` — circular photo backgrounds, accent.
- **Neutrals:** `#e5e4e3` (dividers), `#c2c1c0` (borders), `#929190` (captions/secondary text).

### Typography
- **SplashSerif (Italic):** Used for human-story headlines and pull quotes — *"Meet Selam"*, *"Meet Zeke"*. Warm, approachable italic serif.
- **SplashSerif (Medium):** Section titles like "Big Goals, Significant Change."
- **Gotham Bold:** Impact stats, CTAs, nav items, strong headings.
- **Gotham Medium:** Navigation labels, sub-headings, eyebrows.
- **Gotham Book:** All body copy, captions, descriptive text.
- Type scale flows from ~11px (utility) to 56px (hero stat).

### Backgrounds & Layout
- **Full-bleed photography** is the dominant hero treatment — color-rich, emotionally resonant images of real children.
- **White content sections** separate cleanly below heroes. No textured or patterned backgrounds.
- **Overlaid text on photos** uses drop shadows or white color only — no overlay blocks or gradient films.
- **Section width:** Content centered with generous side margins; ~900–1200px max content width.
- **No gradients** used on background surfaces. Clean flat color only.

### Photography Style
- Children in real environments (schools, water stations).
- Warm-to-neutral color grading; slightly desaturated; never oversaturated.
- Close-up human faces — joyful, candid.
- Location labels ("BENXI, CHINA") appear in Gotham Bold, white, all-caps.

### Cards & Circular Photos
- **Circular photo treatment:** Profile photos cropped round and placed on a colored circle background (orange `#f16322`, green `#005332`, sky `#20bcff`). No card shadow — the colored circle IS the container.
- **Story cards:** Centered layout — circle photo, SplashSerif italic name, Gotham Book description, blue CTA button.

### Buttons
- **Primary CTA:** Sky blue `#20bcff` fill, white Gotham Bold all-caps text, no rounded corners (or very slight ~2px radius), no border.
- **Outlined / Ghost:** White border + white text on dark/photo backgrounds. E.g. "SEE WHERE WE WORK."
- **Donate button:** Outlined white border in the sky-blue nav.
- **Hover:** Deepen to `#0092d2`. No scale transform.
- **No pill/capsule buttons.** Buttons are slightly rectangular with minimal radius.

### Navigation
- **Top utility bar:** Very small Gotham, gray/dark background — BLOG, CONTACT, NEWSLETTER SIGNUP, social icons.
- **Main nav:** Sky blue `#20bcff` background, white Gotham Medium all-caps labels. Splash drop logo top-left. DONATE outlined button top-right.
- **No mega-menu visible.** Single-level horizontal nav.

### Borders & Dividers
- Borders are rare and subtle — `#e5e4e3` or `#c2c1c0` only.
- No heavy card shadow system; Splash uses flat layout.
- Outlined button variant uses `2px solid white` or `2px solid #20bcff`.

### Shadows
- Very minimal. `0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)` maximum for interactive cards.
- No material/elevation shadow system.

### Animation & Interaction
- No animation observed. Hover states shift color deeper (sky → deep blue).
- Assumed standard CSS transitions ~150ms ease.

### Corner Radii
- Buttons: ~2–4px (nearly square).
- Circular photos: `border-radius: 50%`.
- No rounded cards.

