## ICONOGRAPHY

### Icon Font
Splash uses **Font Awesome 4.x** as its icon system. The webfont (`fontawesome-webfont.woff2`) is included in `fonts/`. Use via `font-family: 'FontAwesome'` or via standard `<i class="fa fa-*">` markup (load the CSS from CDN).

### Logo Drop Icon
The **water drop** is Splash's signature mark — used as a standalone favicon/app icon (white on sky blue background) and as part of all logo lockups. It is a custom outline-style drop shape, not a FontAwesome icon.

### Logo Variants
| File | Usage |
|---|---|
| `assets/Splash-Logo-Blue-on-White.jpg` | Default — stacked, blue drop + "Splash" wordmark |
| `assets/Splash-Logo-Horizontal-on-White.png` | Horizontal lockup for wide headers |
| `assets/Splash-Logo-White-on-Blue.png` | Reversed — use on blue/dark backgrounds |
| `assets/Splash-Drop-White-on-Blue.png` | Icon only — app icon, favicon, small contexts |

### Usage Rules
- No emoji used as icons.
- FontAwesome for UI chrome (social links, location pins, arrows, etc.)
- Custom water drop SVG for logo contexts only — do not substitute with generic icon sets.
- Location pin on website uses FontAwesome map-marker (`\f041`).

